title: Match details on the web won't load
body:
Match details never load past this point. 
I know this is a recurrent problem, but none of the suggested fixes I found on the web worked for me

 I tried:

- refreshing the link.
- shift + f5 to clear the cache.
- several chrome extensions, none of them worked, some of them even seemed sketchy.
- loading other peoples match histories (only match histories from the NA server loaded, possibly other servers aswell but couldn't find any links).
- using other browsers.

I have had this problem for quite a while now, so I decided to make this post even though it's a known problem, if anyone knows another solution, please post below.

sincerely,
A salty challenjour smurf

replies.body:
As you mentioned in your post, this is a known issue that we're looking into, but have no solution for at the moment. If you'd like to, feel free to report this on our [**Bug Tracker**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) for more visibility.

Let me know if you have any questions.
